A FAQ will be made available, but meanwhile ...

- Read the header files for function prototypes. They're pretty
  self explanatory
  
- Don't forget to call gtk_init () before you do anything with
  a function call to Gtk
  
- Mounting and unmounting stuff, and things to do with the
  "registry" will probably require root access.

- The "access" module requires the festival framework ( externally )

